data.description: Back on market, buyers funds fell through. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own this gorgeous home site in the highly desired city of MacClenny! Sitting on a gorgeous 3.19 acres is a 4 bedroom, 2 bath mobile home with custom upgrades. As you enter the property on your fully gravel driveway, you'll be charmed by the beautiful large oak trees and one of a kind stocked pond with an island. This is all within a completely fenced parcel. You will have two large storage/workshop buildings, one has a covered carport for all your belongings.  The property is zoned as RCMH!, allowing you to place or build a total of 3 homes or mobile homes on the land for extra income or family. The parcel also comes with a 4'' well that is currently in use and a 2' well not being used
